description:
Your gear is an extension of your true power! And with the Equipment Pack, you'll definitely show any baddies what's up! The Equipment Pack also includes 5 scouts!

The Equipment Pack includes:
- Eye Mask Set
- Protruding Spirit
- Fallen Neptune
- 5x Scouts (Plutia, Peashy, Kei Jinguji, Mina Nishizawa, Chika Hakozaki
